drm/i915/psr: Timestamps for PSR entry and exit interrupts.

Timestamps are useful for IGT tests that trigger PSR exit and/or wait for
PSR entry.

v2: Removed seqlock (Ville)
    Removed erroneous warning in irq loop (Chris)

